      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/4/5/3",
      "text": [
        ": قلت له: أرأيت ما كان وما هو كائن إلى يوم القيامة أليس كان في علم الله تعالى؟ قال: فقال: بلى قبل أن يخلق السماوات والارض"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "3. [3/340] al-Tawhid: My father from Sa’d from Ibn Hashim from Ibn Abi Umayr from Ibn Hazim from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام. He (Ibn Hazim) said: I said to him (the Imam): Consider all that which was and is to be up to the Day of Judgment - was it not in the knowledge of Allah the Elevated? He said: Yes. Before He created the Heavens and the Earth."
        ]
      }
    },
